PEtALS Enterprise Service Bus
-----------------------------
PEtALS provides a leading open source Enterprise Service Bus (ESB) to support 
your Service Oriented Infrastructure.
PEtALS is a lightweight, highly distributed and scalable platform for both 
A2A and B2B integration.
Thanks to its specific distributed architecture and the tools provided, 
PEtALS offers a very competitive integration solution with support of a large 
number of protocols, formats and integration features.


PEtALS URLs
-----------

Home Page:      http://petals.ow2.org/
Downloads:      http://petals.ow2.org/download.html
Documentation:  http://petals.ow2.org/documentation.html
Release Notes:  http://petals.ow2.org/releasenotes.html
Bug Tracking:   http://forge.objectweb.org/tracker/?group_id=213


Getting Started
---------------
To find out how to get started check the tutorials and screencasts on the website.
You can also read the 2 minutes tour http://petals.ow2.org/twominutes.html

Many thanks for using OW2 PEtALS ESB.

Enjoy!
The PEtALS Team